Description :
        A magazine shoot for Eun-dan, formerly a mangdol and currently a photographer, and Won-hae, a popular model.The atmosphere is getting warmer as he removes his hat due to his short pants.Won-hae has been a fan of Eun-dan since he was a mangdol and still is now, so he goes straight ahead, but Eun-dan feels that such Won-hae is a burden.Original Webtoon:Ridibooks, Naver Series, Bomtoon, LezhinOfficial Translations:Thai, T.Chinese
